Edusight is an India-focused, integrated web and mobile platform offering Kâ€“12 students, parents, teachers, and administrators holistic analytics spanning academic performance, physical health, and psychological wellbeing. Leveraging AI and validated assessment frameworks, Edusight delivers personalized career guidance, real-time alerts, and rich dashboards that transform fragmented student data into actionable insights aligned with Indiaâ€™s National Education Policy (NEP 2020).
âœ… Vision
To unlock the full potential of every Indian student by providing deep, data-driven self-awareness and AI-powered educational guidance that inspires informed, personalized, and future-ready learning journeys.
âœ… Mission
To build a scalable and trusted analytics ecosystem that:
Â·	Offers personalized insights into student strengths, challenges, and aspirations
Â·	Equips schools with tools to benchmark performance and improve outcomes
